Goal: R2-A pl-lite/decompose-only on H8 foreach-copy. Produce four TypeScript files that satisfy TASK.md and spec.cjs. No retry loop and no completion gate; scoring is external.

flow:
  prompt: Read TASK.md and spec.cjs in the current working directory. Use your read tool. Reply with a concise numbered contract covering the four required files and the oracle's pass criteria.

  prompt: Implement only src/user.ts according to TASK.md. Use nullish coalescing for defaults. Do not use ||. Reply "ok" when written.

  prompt: Implement only src/product.ts according to TASK.md. Use nullish coalescing for defaults. Do not use ||. Reply "ok" when written.

  prompt: Implement only src/order.ts according to TASK.md. Use nullish coalescing for defaults. Do not use ||. Reply "ok" when written.

  prompt: Implement only src/invoice.ts according to TASK.md. Use nullish coalescing for defaults. Do not use ||. Reply "ok" when written.
